quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  17,23,"Iseyya d Mass ik: ur tâabdem siwa Neppa, elhut ar imawlan. Ma, $uôek wesser yiwen, ne$ ma wessren i sin, ur asen qqaô: \"ttfuh\"! Ur ten ppara. Mmeslay asen s lkyasa"
  17,24,"Zger fellasen tacvat n lmaênana. Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ëun fellasen, akken iyi d ssekren d amejtuê"
  17,25,"Mass nnwen Yif akw akken Issen, i illan deg iman nnwen. Ma telham, Neppa, s tidep, Ipsemmiê wid isteôoiâen"
  17,26,"Efk i llezm ik amur is, akw i ume$bun akked win d ibbwi ubrid. Ur pjeggiê d ajeggeê"
  17,27,"Ijeggaêen, s tidep, d atmaten n Cciîan. Cciîan ijhel ar Mass is"
  17,28,"Ma tfuôqev ten, tôe$bev u tegguniv aêunu s$uô Mass ik, ini yasen awal aéidan"
  17,29,"Ur pcuddu afus ik ar yiri k, ur as berru aîas, mulac a ppu$alev d ambaûi, d ame$bun"
  17,30,"S tidep, Mass ik I$ennu win i S ihwan, u Iwezzen. Neppa, s tidep, Ipwali, Issen imdanen iS"